Beispiel
~~~~~~~~
Das folgende Beispiel gibt einen Text an Position 10/10 mit Farbe Blau aus.


Pascal:
----------------------------------------------------------
        PROCEDURE WriteSomething;

        VAR
          Font : TPixFont;

        BEGIN
          Font.Init (Get8x16FontPtr, 8, 16);
          Font.SetColor (LightBlue);
          Font.WriteXY (10, 10, 'Aber hallo !');
          Font.Done;
        END;
----------------------------------------------------------


C:
----------------------------------------------------------
        void WriteSomething ()
        {
            HFONT Font;

            Font = PixFontInit (Get8x16FontPtr, 8, 16);
            PixFontSetColor (Font, LightBlue);
            PixFontWriteXY (Font, 10, 10, "Aber hallo !");
            PixFontDone (Font);
        }
----------------------------------------------------------



